#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:283 8f8713703d5349d186d53448c78bdf01
msgid ""
"StackChan board driver: SCS serial servos on UART, RGB and servo power on"
" M5IOE1, Si12T touch, INA226 (battery bus), and onboard NFC "
"(``ST25R3916``) as :class:`unit.nfc.NFCUnit`."
msgstr "StackChan 板级驱动：包括 UART 上的 SCS 串口舵机、M5IOE1 上的 RGB 和舵机供电、Si12T 触摸、INA226（电池总线），以及作为 :class:`unit.nfc.NFCUnit` 的板载 NFC（``ST25R3916``）。"

#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:285 562ff4914b034e0ebdac315ba38b235e
msgid ""
"The class is a **singleton**; always construct with the same ``i2c`` and "
"``uart`` ids."
msgstr "该类是**单例**；请始终使用相同的 ``i2c`` 和 ``uart`` id 进行构造。"

