#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:290 9934bc59fe9547558069d5d241755416
msgid ""
"After init, the instance exposes ``nfc`` (a :class:`unit.nfc.NFCUnit`—see"
" `NFC Unit <../unit/nfc.html>`__ for the complete API), ``touch``, "
"``i2c``, and low-level ``servo`` (``Scscl`` instance) for advanced use."
