#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:355 a50d3ea00b01445b87ee98a9273c7c1e
msgid ""
"Move the given servo to ``angle_deg`` (degrees). Use about **-135°~135°**"
" for the X axis (``SERVO_ID_X`` / pan) and **0°~90°** for the Y axis "
"(``SERVO_ID_Y`` / tilt)."
msgstr "将指定舵机移动到 ``angle_deg``（度）。X 轴（``SERVO_ID_X`` / 平移）建议范围约为 **-135°~135°**，Y 轴（``SERVO_ID_Y`` / 俯仰）建议范围为 **0°~90°**。"

#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:358 40fa86d931c54b95a3060259b900a311
msgid "Target angle in degrees (**-135~135** for X, **0~90** for Y)."
msgstr "目标角度（X 为 **-135~135**，Y 为 **0~90**）。"

#: ../../source/controllers/stackchan.rst:359 05bdc98beaba4900ae295517e19f2f5b
msgid ""
"Move time (ms) passed to the controller; ``0`` means the time parameter "
